-- MOVES-Jon Weiss to join hedge fund Candlewood Investment 
-- 
-- Thu Jul 24, 2014 05:56PM EDT
-- None



July 24 (Reuters) - Former Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc <RBS.L> executive Jon Weiss will join hedge fund Candlewood Investment Group LP, Bloomberg reported, citing a person familiar with the matter.

Weiss will join as managing partner and money manager later this year, the report said. (http://bloom.bg/1nF09H9) He was global head of a special situations group at RBS and left this month as the company prepares to wind down the distressed unit, Bloomberg Buisnessweek reported last week.  (http://buswk.co/1lAXp7P) Candlewood Investment was not immediately available for comment.   (Bangalore newsroom; moves@thomsonreuters.com)  Keywords: MOVES RBS/JON WEISS